; Recursive Tree
; ────────────────
; A binary fractal tree drawn with recursive procedures.

TO TREE :SIZE
  IF :SIZE < 5 [STOP]
  FORWARD :SIZE
  LEFT 30
  TREE :SIZE * 0.7
  RIGHT 60
  TREE :SIZE * 0.7
  LEFT 30
  BACKWARD :SIZE
END

HIDETURTLE
PENUP
SETY -160
PENDOWN
SETHEADING 0
SETPENCOLOR "green
TREE 90
